---
// Table Playground — dev only, not in sitemap
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Table Playground</title>
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; }
      body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f8fafc; color: #1e293b; }
      h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
      .meta { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
      .section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
      .section h2 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #475569; }
      .section p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

      .table-wrap {
        border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
      }

      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        width: 100%;
      }
      thead { background: #f1f5f9; }
      th, td {
        padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        text-align: left;
      }
      tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f9fafb; }

      /* Toggle styles */
      .nowrap table th,
      .nowrap table td {
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .toggle-bar {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        background: #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
      .toggle-bar label { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500; }
      .badge {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        padding: 2px 8px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-family: monospace;
      }
      .badge-on { background: #bbf7d0; color: #166534; }
      .badge-off { background: #fecaca; color: #991b1b; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Table Playground</h1>
    <p class="meta">測試 nowrap vs wrap 在不同表格內容下的效果 — 縮放瀏覽器寬度觀察差異</p>

    <div class="toggle-bar">
      <label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="nowrap-toggle" checked />
        white-space: nowrap
      </label>
      <span id="badge" class="badge badge-on">ON</span>
    </div>

    <div id="tables">
      <!-- 1. Short content (like your blog) -->
      <div class="section">
        <h2>1. 短內容（你的文章表格）</h2>
        <p>所有 cell 都很短，nowrap 效果好</p>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>工具</th><th>定位</th><th>核心解決問題</th><th>上手難度</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Claude Code 原生</td><td>內建功能，無需安裝</td><td>並行執行、探索前置</td><td>⭐</td></tr>
              <tr><td>OpenSpec</td><td>規格管理框架</td><td>設計決策持久化、可追溯</td><td>⭐⭐</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Superpowers</td><td>完整開發生命週期</td><td>全流程自動化 + TDD 強制</td><td>⭐⭐⭐</td></tr>
              <tr><td>gstack</td><td>多角色 review 框架</td><td>多視角品質把關（20 個角色）</td><td>⭐⭐</td></tr>
              <tr><td>everything-claude-code</td><td>底層效能優化層</td><td>context 持久化 + agent 體質</td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Mixed content -->
      <div class="section">
        <h2>2. 混合內容（短 + 長描述）</h2>
        <p>有一欄是完整句子，nowrap 會讓表格非常寬</p>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>功能</th><th>狀態</th><th>說明</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Plan Mode</td><td>內建</td><td>AI 先探索 codebase、問問題，不修改 source code，輸出計畫讓你確認後再實作</td></tr>
              <tr><td>/simplify</td><td>內建</td><td>自動派三個平行 review agents 找品質問題並修正，適合大型重構後的清理工作</td></tr>
              <tr><td>/batch</td><td>內建</td><td>大規模並行改動，自動拆成 5-30 個 task，每個在獨立 git worktree 執行</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Many columns -->
      <div class="section">
        <h2>3. 多欄位比較表</h2>
        <p>6 欄以上，不管 wrap 還是 nowrap 都會超出 mobile</p>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>工具</th><th>語言</th><th>安裝方式</th><th>License</th><th>Stars</th><th>最後更新</th><th>維護者</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Claude Code</td><td>TypeScript</td><td>npm</td><td>Proprietary</td><td>N/A</td><td>2026-03</td><td>Anthropic</td></tr>
              <tr><td>OpenSpec</td><td>YAML/MD</td><td>git clone</td><td>MIT</td><td>1.2k</td><td>2026-02</td><td>Community</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Superpowers</td><td>Shell</td><td>curl | bash</td><td>Apache 2.0</td><td>3.4k</td><td>2026-03</td><td>Core team</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Long single-column values -->
      <div class="section">
        <h2>4. 長指令/路徑</h2>
        <p>cell 裡有長指令或 URL，nowrap 合理但會很寬</p>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>指令</th><th>用途</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><code>claude --dangerously-skip-permissions</code></td><td>跳過權限檢查，CI/CD 用</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>CLAUDE_CODE_MAX_TURN_TOKENS=50000 claude</code></td><td>限制單次回應 token 數</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>gh pr create --title "feat: add mermaid" --body "..."</code></td><td>建立 PR</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Two-column simple -->
      <div class="section">
        <h2>5. 簡單兩欄</h2>
        <p>最常見的 key-value 表格，wrap 和 nowrap 差異不大</p>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>設定</th><th>值</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>theme</td><td>catppuccin-mocha</td></tr>
              <tr><td>language</td><td>zh-TW</td></tr>
              <tr><td>deploy</td><td>Cloudflare Pages</td></tr>
              <tr><td>framework</td><td>Astro 6</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      const toggle = document.getElementById('nowrap-toggle');
      const badge = document.getElementById('badge');
      const container = document.getElementById('tables');

      function update() {
        if (toggle.checked) {
          container.classList.add('nowrap');
          badge.textContent = 'ON';
          badge.className = 'badge badge-on';
        } else {
          container.classList.remove('nowrap');
          badge.textContent = 'OFF';
          badge.className = 'badge badge-off';
        }
      }

      toggle.addEventListener('change', update);
      update();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
